data.description: You have a wonderful opportunity, with a bonus structure, to own a property that is remodeled, offering you a total of four bedrooms and two bathrooms. The front home has a remodeled kitchen, a remodeled bathroom and three bedrooms; and, the bonus space has a spacious living area, a remodeled bathroom, an updated mini kitchen, and one bedroom. We look forward to you visiting this home to appreciate the desirable qualities offered for your enjoyment. Action item, take a moment to share the desirable qualities about this wonderful opportunity with neighbors, friends, co-workers, and family. Buyer(s) is expected to research and verify square footage and other property details and information.
